u.seg: the moon above, the moon below

ob me tu gob tii mōn le bwe
the high moon, the low moon

nab tii ōl ta mre ōl ta fyan
you lot, don't make noise here
I will draw the high moon, the low moon
nab tii ōl ta mre , ōl ta fyan
the high moon, the low moon, say it loud so that he hears
ōl ta mre , ōl ta fyan , gob gile van mile rō abo longone
the moon that we were talking about
mun ia we yumi stap storian lo hem
the moon above, the moon which goes down

the foreigner here now, they are drawing for him
ii en nga ngele ru lam tieb vane

ru lam tii tieb rō ru mwe se
me, I drew three, hers are two yet
nō nam tii mwee siel , nge san go ru mwee lō bwe
